height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":19612,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/07\/26\/no-adhan-eid-nawafil-salat\/","url_meta":{"origin":19591,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Eid: No call to prayer for Eid, voluntary prayers","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 26, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Jabir ibn Samurah reported: I performed the Eid prayers with the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, more than once, without announcing the two calls to prayer. Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 887 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Muslim Al-Tirmidhi said, \u201cThis is acted upon by the scholars among\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":19614,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/07\/26\/salat-al-eid-then-khutbah\/","url_meta":{"origin":19591,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Eid: The Prophet prays Eid, then gives sermon","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 26, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Abbas reported: I witnessed the prayer on the day of Eid al-Fitr with the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, and Abu Bakr, Umar, and Uthman, may Allah be pleased with them. They performed the prayer before the sermon, then would deliver the sermon. Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":19324,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/06\/14\/hasan-obedience-to-muslim-leaders\/","url_meta":{"origin":19591,"position":3},"title":"Hasan on Leaders: Obedience to corrupt rulers is difficult, but necessary","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 14, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Rajab reported: Hasan al-Basri, may Allah have mercy on him, said regarding the rulers, \u201cThey take charge of five matters: the Friday prayer, the congregational prayers, the Eid celebration, guarding the frontiers, and the legal punishments. By Allah, the religion will not be upheld without them, even if they\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":4288,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/08\/05\/fajr-rakaat-light\/","url_meta":{"origin":19591,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Fajr: The Prophet would sometimes pray lightly","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 5, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, would sometimes perform two cycles of prayer before the dawn prayer so lightly that I would say to myself, \"Did he recite Surat al-Fatihah?\" Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 1165, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 724 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi\u00a0(authenticity agreed upon)\u00a0according to Al-Bukhari and Muslim\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":15682,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/08\/14\/shorter-surahs-mid-day-salat\/",